; the internal split-horizon zone for fairlane.tetra.cool. mirrors the mesa zone: this resolver's
; own IP, the edge ingress VIP, and a block of one A record per fleet host at its own hostIp
; (all substituted by nix replaceVars, see mesa.tetra.cool.zone.in for the per-host-record
; rationale and the placeholder-in-comments gotcha). the wildcard answers every other name under
; this zone from the edge VIP. serial is static (1) because this zone is generated, never
; hand-edited or transferred.
$TTL 300
$ORIGIN fairlane.tetra.cool.
@   IN SOA ns.fairlane.tetra.cool. hostmaster.fairlane.tetra.cool. (
        1          ; serial
        3600       ; refresh
        900        ; retry
        604800     ; expire
        300 )      ; negative cache ttl
    IN NS  ns.fairlane.tetra.cool.
ns  IN A   @nsIp@
@   IN A   @edgeVip@
*   IN A   @edgeVip@
@hostRecords@
